Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:18.04,SongChn,,0,0,0,,风儿传递着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:24.05,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K90}ka{\K80}ze {\K60}ga {\K50}ha{\K50}ko{\K50}bu  {\K120}{\K65}ka{\K65}su{\K65}ka {\K60}na {\K60}se{\K40}se{\K40}ra{\K60}gi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:24.05,SongJap,,0,0,0,,風が運ぶ かすかなせせらぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:24.05,SongChn,,0,0,0,,细细的溪流声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:35.47,SongChn,,0,0,0,,你看闪闪发光的湖面
