Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:35.47,SongJap,,0,0,0,,ほら まぶしく光る湖は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:49.91,SongChn,,0,0,0,,成为镜子映出那天失去的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:42.67,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K120}ano {\K60}hi {\K70}ni {\K60}{\K50}na{\K40}ku{\K40}shi{\K60}ta {\K60}mo{\K50}no {\K60}wo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:42.67,SongJap,,0,0,0,,あの日に失くしたものを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:49.91,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K60}utsu{\K60}shi{\K60}da{\K60}su {\K50}{\K40}ka{\K40}ga{\K60}mi {\K200}ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:49.91,SongJap,,0,0,0,,映し出す鏡に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:59.89,SongChn,,0,0,0,,幸福一定和悲哀很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:59.89,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K80}kit{\K60}to {\K30}shi{\K30}a{\K20}wa{\K20}se {\K200}wa {\K80}{\K60}ka{\K50}na{\K50}shi{\K50}mi {\K30}ni {\K30}ni{\K30}tei{\K90}ru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:59.89,SongJap,,0,0,0,,きっと幸せは 哀しみに似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:07.93,SongChn,,0,0,0,,闭上心灵的瞳眸
